grdcheat.txt697                        -=-=-> Code Eliminator <-=-=-=-

   The following patch will remove password requirement from GridIron.
   After applying patch enter any three letter code to gain access.

   Using Newzap:  In file C:football, Sector 218, Byte 1E0

                  Currently it should be a 66, change it to 67.

                  Save and your done.

   Using Other Zappers:   In file C:football or disk

                          Search for hex string "660C13FC0001"

                          Change 66 to 67.

                          Save and your done.
- More (Y)/N/NS? y

